=== The clj (clojure) type ===                                    {{{1

  This type is for all sorts of clojure-based application frameworks,
  like noir.

  The template is found in >> lib/type.clj.bash <<.  Feel free to
  fork, improve etc.

  The command used to install dependencies is >> lein deps <<.


  === Options ===                                                 {{{2

    These can be passed to >> nap new <<.

    clj.server      Currently only used for the generated nginx
                    Reverse proxy configuration file.             TODO
    clj.port        Exported as PORT to be used by clj.cmd.
    clj.cmd         Optional.  The command used to start the server.
                    The default is 'lein run :prod'.
                                                                  }}}2
                                                                  }}}1

--

